s/nandi_awards.aspx|title = Nandi Awards of Year 2009| publisher= greenmangos.net |accessdate= 12 February 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n||8||2010||''[[Manasara (2010 film)|Manasara]]''||[[Sri Divya]], [[Bhanu Chander]], George Vincent, Ramaraju ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-manasara.html|title=Telugu Movie review - Manasara.|website=idlebrain}}</ref>\n|-\n||9||2011||''[[Nuvvila]]''||Havish, Ajay, [[Yami Gautam]], [[Vijay Deverakonda]], [[Prasad Barve]]||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.idlebrain.com/movie/archive/mr-nuvvila.html| title = Telugu Movie review - Nuvvila| publisher= [[idlebrain.com]] |accessdate=11 February 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n||10||2012||''[[Avunu (film)|Avunu]]''||[[Harshvardhan Rane]], [[Shamna Kasim|Poorna]], Ravi Babu||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?Section=Movies&ID=270776&subcatg=&keyword=regional&nid=270776 |title=Avunu movie review|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120929001845/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?Section=Movies&ID=270776&subcatg=&keyword=regional&nid=270776 |date=29 September 2012|archive-date=29 Sep 2012|work=NDTV movies}}</ref>\n|-\n||11||2014||''[[Laddu Babu]]''||Allari Naresh, Bhumika Chawla, Poorna, [[Kota Srinivasa Rao]]||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| || <ref>{{cite web| title =  Laddu Babbu Telugu Movie Review | url = http://venditera.in/reviews/laddu-babbu-telugu-movie-review | publisher = Venditera.in| accessdate =2014-04-18}}</ref>\n|-\n||12||2015||''[[Avunu 2]]''|| [[Harshvardhan Rane]], Poorna, Ravi Babu, [[Sanjjanaa]]||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||\n|-\n||13||2018||''[[Adhugo]]''|| Ravi Babu||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||\n|-\n|14||2019|| ''[[Aaviri]]''|| Ravi Babu||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| ||\n|}\n\n===As actor===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- \n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Notes \n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1998 || ''[[Maavidaakulu]]'' || Muddu Krishna ||\n|-\n| '